quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  7,59,My sent Noah jeho ludia saying O moj ludia kult GOD ona nie have inak god Him. Ja fear for ona retribution awesome dni
  7,60,leaders jeho ludia said My see ona bol daleko astray
  7,61,He said O moj ludia ja je astray; ja bol posol Lord universe
  7,62,Ja deliver ona odkaz moj Lord ja radit ona ja zauzlit GOD co ona nie zauzlit
  7,63,Je it i vela z zazrak ze reminder pojdem ona tvoj Lord clovek ona warn ona lead ona do righteousness ze ona attain zlutovanie
  7,64,They zamietnut him. Consequently my saved him those him do ark my drowned those zamietnut our revelations; they je blind